SerialModemGateway

public SerialModemGateway(java.lang.String id,
                          java.lang.String comPort,
                          int baudRate,
                          java.lang.String manufacturer,
                          java.lang.String model)
Constructor for a serially connected gsm modem or phone.

Parameters:
id - Your own ID for addressing this gateway.
comPort - The comm port to which this modem is connected. For example, COM1 or /dev/ttyS1.
baudRate - The baud rate of the serial connection.
manufacturer - The manufacturer, for example "Nokia".
model - The model, for example "6130"
